<!-- RECORD -->
<section class="lib-record">
  <div class="lib-record-orn vc-orn-rule reveal"><span class="mk">§</span></div>
  <div class="lib-record-rubric reveal">What is on the Record</div>
  <h2 class="lib-record-h reveal">The ledger, <em>so far.</em></h2>
  <p class="lib-record-intro reveal">
    What follows is what the public record holds today. Where the state&rsquo;s account is incomplete, the entry is marked <em>Open.</em> The Enclave will not invent what it does not know &mdash; and will not forget what it does.
  </p>

  <div class="lib-ledger reveal">
    <div class="lib-ledger-row">
      <div class="date">Entry I<em>Early April · MMXXV</em></div>
      <p class="entry">
        Tamion Kenon, a <strong>34-year-old</strong> Black man, is taken into the custody of the <strong>Fort Bend County</strong> jail system. He is alive. He is awaiting his day in court.
      </p>
      <div class="status">From the docket<em>On the record</em></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lib-ledger-row terminal">
      <div class="date">Entry II<em>3 April · MMXXV</em></div>
      <p class="entry">
        Within roughly forty-eight hours of being booked in, Tamion is found <em>unresponsive in his cell.</em> He is pronounced dead. He never reaches the arraignment that was being prepared for him.
      </p>
      <div class="status">Manner of death<em>Pending</em></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lib-ledger-row">
      <div class="date">Entry III<em>The days after</em></div>
      <p class="entry">
        An outside investigation is opened. The county begins its own internal review. Tamion&rsquo;s family is told some of what happened, and not told other parts. <em>Gloria, his mother,</em> begins asking the questions the record will not answer on its own.
      </p>
      <div class="status">Inquiry<em>Open · External</em></div>
    </div>

    <div class="lib-ledger-row">
      <div class="date">Entry IV<em>This page</em></div>
      <p class="entry">
        The Enclave files this libation under the Pillar of <em>Emancipated</em> &mdash; the unfinished obligations of freedom. We hold the entry open. We add what is verified. We strike nothing. We remove nothing. <strong>The record remembers.</strong>
      </p>
      <div class="status">Status<em>Kept by the lineage</em></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lib-record-foot reveal">
    Updates to this record are made only with the family&rsquo;s blessing.
    To correct or add to the ledger, write <em>libations@e5enclave.com</em>.
  </div>
</section>


